author: scottbw
msg: Fix for WOOKIE-44 the impl of the sharedDataForKey DWR method was not catching nulls; I've trapped these now and return the "No matching key found" error message as per preferenceForKey().

author: boisvert
msg: Environment variable IGNORE_BUILDFILE can be set to "yes" or "true" to ignore
changes in Buildfile when running tests.
A real timesaver when you're tweaking the Buildfile to get specific tests working.
